'''Zeresenay Berhane Mehari''' (wavutse 1974), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Etiyopiya]] <ref>https://www.buchmesse.de/en/timetable/speaker/zeresenay-berhane-mehari</ref>.  Azwiho kuba umuyobozi wa firime ''zizwi'' cyane Difret na ''Sweetness in Belly'' <ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/interview/378601/</ref>. 

Usibye sinema, ni umwe mu bashinze kandi akaba n'Umuyobozi w'Ibintu by'umwimerere kuri Televiziyo ya Kana, Televiziyo ya mbere yashyizwe ku buntu ku kirere, yigenga  muri [[Etiyopiya]].<ref>https://www.screendaily.com/features/zeresenay-berhane-mehari-difret/5065078.article</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i [[Addis Ababa|Addis Abeba]], muri [[Etiyopiya]] mu muryango ufite barumuna barindwi. Nyuma yaje kwimukira muri [[Amerika]] mu gihe murumuna we na mushiki we bimukiye mu [[Ubuholandi|Buholandi]], undi muvandimwe akaba muri [[Suwede]] .<ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/374847/</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Nyuma yo kwimukira muri [[Amerika]], Mehari yize filime muri kaminuza y’amajyepfo ya California School of Cinematic Arts arangiza impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts.  Mugihe yiga, yashinze isosiyete ikora 'Haile - Addis Pictures'.<ref>https://sffilm.org/event/difret/</ref> 

Yatangiye gukora nkumufasha wibikorwa mubice bibiri: ''Byose kuri Eva'' na ''The seven Year Itch'' muri 2000 ya tereviziyo ya ''Backstory'' . Noneho yabaye umufasha wibikorwa byigice ''M * A * S * H: Comedy Under Fire'' muri 2001 Urutonde ''rwamateka vs.'' ''Hollywood'' <ref>https://www.locarnofestival.ch/LFF/program/archive/person.html?pid=720219&l=en&eid=67</ref>. Nyuma muri 2006, yabaye producer wa ''Leila'' ngufi iyobowe na Hanelle M. Culpepper. Nyuma yumwaka, yakoze firime ye ya mbere ''Coda'' .<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1877993/</ref> 

Mu 2005 yamenyeshejwe na avoka Meaza Ashenafi na murumuna we. Hanyuma hamwe na we, bavumbuye ikibazo cya Hirut Assefa n'umuco wa “telefa” mugihe bakora ubushakashatsi kuri Meaza no gukorera mumuryango we. ''akoresheje'' ibyabaye, yayoboye filime yumukobwa yitwa Difret muri 2014, yungutse ibitekerezo byiza<ref>http://africultures.com/difret-de-zeresenay-berhane-mehari-12973/</ref>.  Umuyobozi mukuru wa firime yari umukinnyi wa filime uzwi cyane muri Hollywood, Angelina Jolie <ref>https://www.buchmesse.de/en/timetable/speaker/zeresenay-berhane-mehari</ref>.  Nubwo yagize amahirwe yo gufata amashusho muri 2009, nyuma yaje gutegereza kugeza muri 2012 gufata amashusho kubera ibibazo byo gukina.<ref>http://www.spilling-the-beans.net/sundance-2014-selection-from-ethiopia-difret-attracts-angelina-jolie-as-exec-producer/</ref> Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Sundance Film Festival muri Mutarama 2013. Filime yatsindiye ibihembo byabitabiriye iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance, iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Berlin, iserukiramuco rya muzika rya Park City, iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Amsterdam ndetse no mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Montreal <ref>http://www.savefilm.org/news/difret-is-ethiopias-official-selection-for-the-academy-awards/</ref>. Icyakora, muri Nzeri 2014, muri Etiyopiya herekanywe bwa mbere ku mugaragaro abayobozi ba filime bavuga ko iyi filime yahaye Meaza 'inguzanyo nyinshi'. Ariko, nyuma yaje kurekurwa n'imanza ebyiri kandi ifite ibigwi muri [[Etiyopiya]].<ref>https://entropymag.org/difret-by-zeresenay-berhane-mehari/</ref>  

Muri 2019, yakoze igice cya kabiri, ''Sweetness in the Belly'', film ya kabiri yakinnye na Dakota Fanning na Yahya Abdul-Mateen II .  Cyari gifite umwanya wambere mugice cya Discovery cyumunsi mukuru wa firime ya Toronto. Filime yahinduwe nigitabo cyizina rimwe ryanditswe na Camilla Gibb<ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/378291/</ref> . 

